Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Further bugfixes in the upgrade of News Items to a flexible schema.
- Moved hardcoded table style to stylesheet
- Made table based layouts better look when combined with div based ones
- Fixed edit form and 'editLayouts.py' script to avoid  namespace clash
  on request variable 'layout_id' and make it actually possible to use several
  flexible layouts on the same document type
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Moved jscalendar lang/ subdir to calendar-lang/ to avoid name collisions.
- the modify transition is called at modification time for all documents that
  have it defined in their wf (not only in so called 'workspaces')

